hadiths[173]{hadithnumber,text}:
3418,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di. (unkey walid mohtaram) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha to kaha : (merey betey) Abdullah ney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di hai. aap ney farmaya : Abdullah sey kaho ke us sey ruju kerey. phir usey chodey rakhey yahan tak ke wo apney haiz sey paak ho jaey, phir usey doosra haiz aaye, phir jab wo haiz sey pak ho to agar chahey to usey jima (sambhog) karney sey qabl Talaq dey dey aur agar chahey to usey apney nikah mein rakhey. bilashuba ye hai wo sahih waqt jo Allah Taala ney aurton ko Talaq deney key liye muqarrar kiya hai."
3419,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi. Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kaho ke us sey ruju kerey. phir usey apney paas rakhey yahan tak ke wo pak ho, phir usey haiz aaye, phir wo pak ho. ab iskey baad agar wo chahey to usey rakhey aur chahey to jima (sambhog) sey pehley Talaq dey dey. ye wo sahih waqt hai jo Allah Taala ney aurton ko Talaq deney key liye muqarrar farmaya hai."
3420,"Hazrat Zohri sey puchha gaya ke sahih waqt par Talaq ka kya tariqa hai? unhoney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Salim ney (apney walid mohtaram) Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) is par ghussey huye aur farmaya : wo us sey ruju kerey. phir usey apney paas rakhey yahan tak ke usey eik aur haiz aaye, phir wo pak ho. ab agar us ka khayal baney to tuhur (paaki) ki haalat mein baghair jima (sambhog) kiye usey Talaq dey dey. ye sahih waqt par Talaq hai jaisa ke Allah Taala ney hukm nazil farmaya hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey apni biwi sey ruju kar liya, aur jo Talaq mainey usey (haiz ki haalat mein) di thi, wo Talaq hi samjhi."
3421,Hazrat abu-Zubair ki mojudgi mein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya ke aap ka us aadmi key barey mein kya khayal hai jisney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq de-di? wo farmaney lagey : Abdullah bin umr ney apni biwi ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to (yun) kaha : Abdullah bin umr ney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey chahiye ke wo us sey ruju kerey. aur aap ney meri biwi merey paas bhej di aur farmaya : jab ye haiz sey pak ho to phir Talaq dey ya apney nikah mein rakhey. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat padhi : « { یٰآَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ اِذَا طَلَّقْتُمْ النِّسَاءَ … }  aey Nabi ! jab tum aurton ko Talaq deney lago to unhen unki iddat key shuru waqt mein Talaq do.
3422,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Allah Taala key farman : « { یٰآَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ اِذَا طَلَّقْتُمْ النِّسَاءَ فَطَلَّقْوْھُنَّ لِعِدَّتِھِنَّ … } » mein « { لِعِدَّتِھِنَّ … } » sey murad « قُبُلِ عِدَّتِھِنَّ » hai, yani iddat key aaghaz mein (Talaq do)."
3423,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Talaq sunnat ye hai ke tuhur ki haalat mein jima kiye baghair eik Talaq di jaey, phir jab wo haiz key baad pak ho to usey dusri Talaq dey dey, phir jab usey haiz aaye aur wo haiz sey pak ho jaey to usey teesri Talaq dey dey, phir uskey baad wo aurat eik haiz iddat guzaregi. (raawi hadees) Hazrat Aamash ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai sey puchha to unhoney bhi aisey hi kaha."
3424,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Talaq sunnat ye hai ke aurat ko tuhur ki haalat mein baghair jima key (eik ) Talaq dey dey.
3425,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaey aur aap ko uski ittilaa ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : Abdullah sey kaho us sey ruju kerey. jab wo ghusl haiz karey to usey uski haalat par rehney dey yahan tak ke usey doosra haiz aaye, phir jab wo dusrey haiz sey pak ho kar ghusl karey to wo us sey jima na kerey. phir chahey to Talaq de-dey aur chahey to apney nikah mein rakhey. ye hai wo sahih waqt jis mein Allah Taala ney aurton ko Talaq deney ka hukm diya hai."
3426,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney zikr hui to aap ney farmaya : usey kaho ke us sey ruju kerey. phir tuhur ya hamal ki haalat mein usey Talaq dey.
3427,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq de-di thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki biwi ko un ki taraf lota diya yahan tak ke unhoney usey tuhur ki haalat mein Talaq di.
3428,"Hazrat Yunus bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey us aadmi key barey mein puchha jo apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey bethey to unhoney farmaya : to Abdullah bin umr ko janta hai? us ney bhi apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey uski baabat puchha to aap ney usey ruju karney ka hukm diya ke phir wo sahih waqt par Talaq dey. mainey arz kya : kya wo Talaq shumar hogi ? aap ney farmaya : aur kya ? agar wo sahih waqt par Talaq deney sey aajiz raha aur us ney ye nadani kar li ( to kya tera khayal hai wo shumar na hogi ) ?"
3429,Hazrat Yunus bin Juber ney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey arz kya ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di. (tu ab kya kerey?) farmaney lagey : kya to Abdullah bin umr ko janta hai? us ney bhi apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq de-di thi. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ye masla poochhney key liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye to aap ney hukm diya ke wo us sey ruju kerey. phir sahih waqt mein naey sirey sey Talaq dey. mainey kaha : jab aadmi apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq de-dey to kya wo Talaq shumar hogi? farmaya : aur kya? agar-che wo sahih waqt par Talaq deney sey aajiz raha aur us ney nadani ka muzahira kya.
3430,"Hazrat Mehmood bin Labid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik aadmi key barey mein bataya gaya jisney apni biwi ko ikatthi teen talaaqein de-di thin. aap ghussey ki haalat mein uth khadey huye aur farmaya, kya meri mojudgi mein Allah Taala ki kitab sey khela jata hai? yahan tak ke eik aadmi khada ho kar kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main usey qatl na kar dun?"
3431,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Uwemir Ajlani (Raziallahu anhu) (apney sardar ) Hazrat Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur kaha : Aasim ! bataiye agar eik aadmi apni biwi key sath kisi aadmi ko paey to kya wo usey qatl kar dey ? phir usey log ( qisaas mein) qatl kar dengey, phir wo kya karey ? aap merey liye ye masla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochein. chunanche Hazrat Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey sawalaat ko napasand farmaya aur unhen maayub samjha yahan tak ke Hazrat Aasim par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hui baat bahut shaaq guzri . phir jab Aasim apney ghar wapis aaye to Uwemir ney aa kar kaha : Aasim ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen kya kaha hai? Aasim kehney lagey : to merey paas koi achi chiz nahin ley kar aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney terey is sawal ko napasand farmaya hai. Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! main to baaz nahin aaunga yahan tak ke main ye masla khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochhun. Uwemir aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon key darmiyan bethey they. aur unhoney ( aa kar) kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap farmaain eik aadmi apni biwi key sath koi aur aadmi dekh leta hai to kya wo usey qatl kar dey ? phir aap usey qatl kar dengey, ya wo kya karey ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey aur teri biwi key barey mein wahi utar chuki hai, lihaza to ja aur usey ley aa. Hazrat Sahal ney kaha : phir unhoney aapas mein liaan kya. us waqt main bhi dusrey logon key sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas mojud tha. jab Uwemir liaan sey farigh huye to kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar ab bhi mein usey apney nikah mein rakhun tab to goya mainey is par jhoot baandha tha. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm deney sey pehley hi unhoney usey teen talaaqein de-din."
3432,Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya : main aale-Khalid mein sey eik aurat hun. merey khawind ney mujhey ( aakhiri ) Talaq bhej di hai. mainey khawind key ghar walon sey apney liye rihaaish aur ikhrajat talab kiye to unhoney inkar kar diya hai. unhon ( khawind key ghar walon ) ney jawab diya : aey Allah key Rasool ! uskey khawind ney usey teen talaaqein bhej di hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ikhrajat o rihaaish to us (mutallaqa) aurat ko miltey hain jis key khawind ko us sey ruju ka haq hai.
3433,Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aurat ko teen talaaqein ho chuki hun usi doran iddat mein kharcha o rihaaish nahin milengey۔
3434,Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : mujhey (merey khawind) abu-Amr bin Hafs makhzumi ney teen talaaqein de-din. Hazrat Khalid bin waleed (Raziallahu anhu) banu Makhzum key kuch dusrey logon key sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! abu-Amr bin Hafs ney apni biwi Fatima ko teen talaaqein de-di hain to kya usi doran iddat ikhrajat milengey? aap ney farmaya : usey na ikhrajat milengey aur na rihaaish.
3435,"Hazrat Taoos sey manqul hai ke Hazrat abu-Sahba Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey ibne-Abbas ! kya aap nahin jantey ke b-yak waqt teen talaaqein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key daur mubarak mein, neez Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key ibtidaai daur mein, eik Talaq samjhi jati thin? aap ney farmaya : haan."
3436,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha gaya ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi ko teen talaaqein de-din, phir us aurat ney kisi aur mard sey shaadi kar li aur wo uskey sath alehda to huwa lekin jima kiye baghair Talaq dey di, kya ye aurat pehley khawind key liye halal hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, yahan tak ke wo doosra (nikah karney wala) shakhs us aurat ka maza chakhey aur aurat us mard ka maza chakhey ( lazzat jima hasil karen )."
3437,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Rifaa Qarzi (Raziallahu anhu) ki ( sabiqa ) biwi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey ( Rifaa key teen talaaqein deney key baad ) Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber sey nikah kya hai. Allah ki qism ! uskey paas to sirf kapdey key un-baney is kinarey ki tarah hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shayad to dobara Rifaa key nikah mein jana chahti hai? hergiz nahin (ja sakti) yahan tak ke wo tujh sey lazzate-jima hasil karey aur to us sey.
3438,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Rifaa Qarzi (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui jab ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap key paas mojud they. kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main ( pehley) Rifaa Qarzi key nikah mein thi. lekin unhoney mujhey bitta Talaq dey di. mainey ( iddat guzarney key baad ) Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey shaadi kar li. Allah ki qism ! aey Allah key Rasool ! unka uzu to kapdey key is an-buney kinarey ki tarah hai. iskey sath hi usney apni chadar ka eik kinara pakad kar dikhaya. Hazrat Khalid bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bahar darwazey par they. aap ney unhen andar aaney ki ijazat nahin di thi. wo kehney lagey : aey abu-Bakar! aap us aurat ki baat nahin sun rahey? ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bhi wohi kuch keh rahi hai jo kuch ( bahar ) kehti phirti hai. aap ney farmaya : to Rifaa key nikah mein jana chahti hai? to nahin ja sakti yahan tak ke to Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber sey aur wo tujh sey lazzate-jima hasil kerey.
3439,"Hazrat Hammad bin Zaid sey manqul hai ke mainey Ayub sey kaha : kya aap jantey hain ke kisi ney ( أَمْرُکِ بِیَدِکَ ) tera maamla terey ikhtiyar mein hai, , kehney ki surat mein usey teen Talaq kaha ho? siwaye Hazrat Hasan Basri key ? unhoney kaha : nahin, phir kehney lagey : ya Allah ! maaf farmana ( haan ) magar wo hadees jo mujhey Qatada ney Kasir Mola ibn Samra an abi Salma an abi Hurera ki sanad sey bayan ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (ye alfaz kehna ) teen talaaqein hain. (Hazrat Hammad ney kaha : ) main Kasir ko mila aur un sey us hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney us hadees sey la-ilmi zahir ki, phir main Hazrat Qatada key paas gaya aur un sey puri baat zikr ki to unhoney kaha : Kasir bhool gaey. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees munkar hai."
3440,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rifaa ki ( sabiqa ) biwi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar kaha : mujhey merey khawind ney Talaq di. aur Talaq bitta ( teesri Talaq ) di. mainey uskey baad Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber sey nikah kar liya lekin uskey paas to kapdey key pallu ( kinarey ) key siwa kuch nahin hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hans padey aur farmaya : shayad to dobara Rifaa key nikah mein jana chahti hai? to nahin ja sakti yahan tak ke wo tujh sey ( jima kar key) lutf andoz ho aur to us sey lutf andoz ho.
3441,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi ko teen talaaqein dey din, phir us aurat ney kisi aur aadmi sey nikah kar liya lekin us ney usey jima karney sey pehley Talaq dey di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kya wo aurat pehley khawind key liye halal hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin, yahan tak ke ye doosra khawind us sey ( jima kar key) lutf andoz ho jaisa ke pehla khawind lutf andoz hota raha."
3442,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat « غُمَیْصَاء » ya Ramisaa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur apney khawind ki shikayat karney lagi ke wo jima nahin kar sakta. itney mein us ka khawind bhi aa gaya aur us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye jhoot bolti hai. main iskey sath jima karta hun lekin ye apney pehley khawind key paas dobara jana chahti hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : iskey liye ye jayez nahin yahan tak ke to ussey jima kerey.
3443,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aadmi key barey mein, jo apni biwi ko teen talaaqein dey deta hai, phir koi doosra shakhs us sey nikah kar leta hai lekin wo bhi usey hum bistari sey pehley hi Talaq dey deta hai aur wo aurat pehley khawind key yahan wapis jana chahti hai, farmaya : wo nahin ja sakti yahan tak ke doosra khawind us sey jima kerey."
3444,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us aadmi key barey mein puchha gaya jo apni biwi ko teen talaaqein dey deta hai, phir koi aur aadmi us sey nikah kar leta hai, phir wo darwaza band kar key parda latka leta hai lekin jima sey pehley usey Talaq dey deta hai. aap ney farmaya : itney sey wo pehley khawind key liye halal na hogi yahan tak ke doosra khawind us sey jima kerey. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) farmatey hain : ye ( Sufiyan wali sanad Shoba ki mazkura sanad sey) durusti key ziyada laaiq hai (lekin dono ka matn shawahid ki ru sey sahih hai )."
3445,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jism mein rang bharney wali, bharwaney wali, zayed baal milaaney wali aur jisey zayed baal lagaey jaeyn, sood khaney waley aur khilaney waley, Halala karney waley aur jis key liye Halala kya jaey, un sab par lanat farmaai hai."
3446,"Auzai kehtey hain ke mainey Imam Zohri sey us aurat key mutalliq puchha jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey panah maangi thi to unhoney kaha ke mujhey Hazrat Urwa ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey bayan kya hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki kilabi biwi jab aap key paas aai to kehney lagi : main aap sey Allah ki panah mein aati hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to bahut badi zaat ki panah mein aai hai, lihaza apney ghar chali ja."
3447,Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke merey khawind ney mujhey Talaq likh bheji to mainey apney kapdey pehney aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui. aap ney puchha : wo tujhey kitni talaaqein dey chuka hai? mainey kaha : teen. farmaya : phir tujhey kharch waghera nahin milega. to apney chacha zaad bhai ibn Umme-Maktum key ghar iddat guzar. wo na-bina shakhs hai. to uskey haan kapdey bhi utaar sakti hai. jab teri iddat puri ho jaey to mujhey ittila karna. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
3448,Tamim Maula Fatima ney bhi Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey usi qism ki riwayat bayan ki hai.
3449,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : mainey apni biwi ko apney ooper haram kar liya hai. aap ney farmaya : tu ney jhoot kaha. wo tujh par haram nahin, phir ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (یٰآَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ مَا اَحَلَّ اللّٰہُ لَکَ) padhi. aey Nabi ! aap us chiz ko kyon haram kartey hain jo Allah Taala ney aap key liye halal ki hai? haan tujh par sakht tareen kaffara hoga, yani eik ghulam azad karna."
3450,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni zauja mohtarma Hazrat Zainab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ( ziyada der ) thehertey aur unkey paas shehad peetey they. mainey aur Hafsa ney aapas mein mansuba banaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hum mein sey jis key yahan bhi tashrif laeyn wo aap sey kahey ke main aap sey maghafir ki bu paati hun. aap hum mein sey kisi key paas tashrif laye to usney aap sey wohi baat keh di. aap ney farmaya : mainey to Zainab key yahan sey shehad piya hai, dobara nahin piyunga. phir ye aayat utri :  (یٰآَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ مَا اَحَلَّ اللّٰہُ لَکَ) aey Nabi ! aap us chiz ko kyon haram kartey hain jisey Allah Taala ney aap key liye halal kya hai? (aagey aaney waley alfaz ) (ان تتوبآ الی اللہ) main Hazrat Aaisha aur Hafsa Raziallahu anhuma ki taraf ishara hai aur (واذ اسرا النبی الی بعض ازواجہ حدیثا) main baat sey murad aap ka ye farman hai, mainey shehad piya hai ( dobara nahin piyunga). ye sari tafsil Ata ki hadees mein hai."
3451,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik sey riwayat hai ke mainey (apney walid mohtaram ) Hazrat Kaab bin Malik ko apni aap beeti bayan kartey suna, jab wo ghazwa tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey peechey reh gaey. unhoney pura waqia bayan farmaya. phir farmaya is doran mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qaasid merey paas aaya aur kehney laga : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tujhey hukm dey rahey hain ke apni biwi sey alag ho ja. mainey kaha : usey Talaq dey dun ya kya karun? wo kehney laga : nahin, sirf us sey alehda reh, uskey qarib na jana. mainey apni biwi sey kaha : to apney ghar chali ja aur unkey paas reh yahan tak ke Allah Taala us barey mein koi faisla farmaey."
3452,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik sey riwayat hai ke mainey (apney walid mohtaram) Hazrat Kaab bin Malik ko apni aap beeti bayan kartey suna, jab wo ghazwa tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey peechey reh gaey. unhoney pura waqia bayan farmaya. phir farmaya is doran mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qaasid merey paas aaya aur kehney laga : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tujhey hukm dey rahey hain ke apni biwi sey alag ho ja . mainey kaha : usey Talaq dey dun ya kya karun ? wo kehney laga : nahin, sirf us sey alehda reh, uskey qarib na jana. mainey apni biwi sey kaha : to apney ghar chali ja aur unkey paas reh yahan tak ke Allah Taala us barey mein koi faisla farmaey."
3453,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik ney kaha : mainey apney walid mohtaram Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan farmatey suna, aur merey walid un teen logon mein sey eik they jinki tauba qubul hui thi. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aur merey dusrey do sathiyon ko pegham bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tumhen hukm detey hain ke apni aurton sey juda raho. mainey qaasid sey kaha : main usey Talaq dey dun ya kya karun ? us ney kaha : nahin, balke sirf us sey alag reh , uskey qarib na jana. mainey apni biwi sey kaha : to apney meykey chali ja aur unkey paas reh. chunanche wo meykey chali gaee."
3454,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni aap beetii bayan farmatey suna, jab wo ghazwa tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath janey sey reh gaey they. unhoney farmaya ke us doran mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qaasid merey paas aaya aur kehney laga : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tujhey apni aurat sey alag rehney ka hukm irshad farma rahey hain. mainey kaha : usey Talaq dey dun ya kya karun? usney kaha : balke us sey juda reh , qarib na jana. aap ney merey do sathiyon ki taraf bhi yehi pegham bheja . mainey apni biwi sey kaha : to apney meykey chali ja aur unkey paas reh yahan tak ke Allah Taala hamarey barey mein koi faisla farma dey. Maaqil bin Ubedullah ney un ki mukhalifat ki hai."
3455,Hazrat Ubedullah bin Kaab bayan kartey hain ke mainey apney walid mohtaram Hazrat Kaab ko bayan farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aur merey do sathiyon ko pegham bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tum ko apni biwiyon sey alag rehney ka hukm detey hain. mainey qaasid sey kaha : main apni biwi ko Talaq dey dun ya kya karun ? us ney kaha : Talaq nahin balke to us sey ( waqti taur) par alag reh aur uskey qarib na jana. mainey apni biwi sey kaha : apney meykey chali ja aur un mein reh yahan tak ke Allah azz-w-jall koi faisla farmaey. chunanche wo apney meykey chali gaee. Maamar ney (ma'qil ki) mukhalifat ki hai.
3456,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kaab bin Malik apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kartey hain ke us doran mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qaasid merey paas aaya aur kehney laga : apni aurat sey alehda reh. mainey kaha : usey Talaq dey dun? us ney kaha : nahin. lekin uskey qarib na jana. us riwayat mein raawi ney « اِلْحَقِیی بِأَھْلِکِ » apney meykey chali ja. key alfaz zikr nahin kahe.
3457,"Banu Naufal key maula Hazrat Abu-Hasan sey marwi hai ke main aur meri biwi dono ghulam they. mainey usey do talaqein dey di thin, phir hum dono azad kar diye gaey. mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha to unhoney farmaya : agar to us sey ruju kar ley to wo terey paas lot sakti hai aur eik Talaq baqi hogi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney yehi faisla farmaya hai. Maamar ney (Ali bin mubarak ki) mukhalifat ki hai."
3458,"Banu-Nofal key Mola Hazrat abul-Hasan sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya ke eik ghulam ney apni biwi ko do talaaqein dey din, phir wo dono azad ho gaey, kya ab wo dobara us sey shaadi kar sakta hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. saail ney puchha : aap ye kis sey naqal farmatey hain? unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye fatwaa irshad farmaya hai. abdur-Razzaaq ney kaha : ( Abdullah ) ibne-mubarak ney Hazrat Maamar sey kaha : ye Hasan kon hai? us ney bahut bhari pathar uthaya hai."
3459,"Hazrat Kasir bin Saaib bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Banu Qureza key nojawan ladkon ney bayan kya ke hamen jang Qureza key din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney pesh kya gaya to jis ladkey ko ehtilaam hota tha ya uskey zere-naf baal ugey huye they, usey qatl kar diya jata tha aur jis ko ehtilaam nahin hota tha ya jisey zere-naf baal nahin ugey huye they, usey chhod diya jata tha."
3460,"Hazrat Atiya Qarzi sey marwi hai ke jin dino Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney Banu Qureza key barey mein faisla sunaya, main bacha tha. unhen merey barey mein shak huwa (ke baligh hai ya nabaligh ) lekin jab mujhey dekha to merey sharmgah key baal nahin ugey they to mujhey chhod diya gaya. dekh lo ab main tumharey darmiyan mojud hun."
3461,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-Uhad key moqey par mera jayeza liya. main us waqt chaudah saal ka tha. aap ney mujhey jang mein shirkat ki ijazat na di, phir ghazwa khandaq key moqey par jayeza liya to main pandarah saal ka ho chuka tha. aap ney mujhey ijazat dey di."
3462,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen ashkhas sey qalam utha liya gaya hai : sotey shakhs sey yahan tak ke wo jaag padey, nabaligh sey yahan tak ke wo baligh ho jaey aur majnun o pagal sey yahan tak ke usey aql o hosh aa jaey."
3463,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat ko wo baaten maaf farma di hain jo wo apney dilon mein kartey hain, jab tak wo zaban par na laeyn ya un par amal na karen."
3464,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat ko waswasey aur dili khayalat maaf kar diye hain jab tak wo un par amal na karen ya zaban par na laeyn .
3465,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat ko dili waswason aur waqti khayalat maaf farma diye hain jab tak wo in ko zaban par na laeyn ya un par amal na karen.
3466,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka eik Farsi padosi tha jo shorbaa behtareen banata tha. eik din wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya jab ke aap key paas Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi thin. us ney aap ko haath sey ishara kya ke aaiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Aaisha ki taraf ishara farmaya ke ye bhi aayegi to usney haath sey ishara kya ke nahin. do teen dafa aisey hi huwa.
3467,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aamal ka aetbar niyat key sath hai. har aadmi ko uski niyat milegi . chunanche jis shakhs ki hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool ki khatir hogi, usey Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf hijrat hi ka sawab milega aur jis shakhs ki hijrat duniya key husool ya kisi aurat ( sey shaadi ) ki khatir hogi to uski hijrat usi chiz ki taraf hogi jiski taraf us ney hijrat ki."
3468,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dekho ! Allah Taala Quraish key gaali galoch aur laan-taan ko mujh sey kaisey door rakhta hai? wo muzammam ko bura kehtey hain aur muzammam ko lanat kartey hain jab ke main to Muhammad hun. (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam)
3469,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Allah Taala ki taraf sey apni biwiyon ko ikhtiyar deney ka hukm huwa to aap sab sey pehley merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : main tujh sey eik baat karta hun. jawab deney mein jaldi ki zarurat nahin. beshak apney waliden sey mashwara kar lena. (aap ney ye is liye farmaya ke ) aap jantey they ke merey waliden mujhey kabhi bhi aap sey judai ka mashwara nahin dey saktey. phir aap ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : « { یٰآیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ قُلْ لِّاَزْوَاجِکَ اِنْ کُنْتُنَّ … }  aey Nabi ! apni biwiyon sey keh dijiye : agar tum duniya ki zindagi aur zeb o zeenat ki Talib ho to aao main tumhen achey tareeqey sey farigh kar dun …. mainey fauran kaha : kya main is barey mein apney waliden sey mashwara talab karun? main to har haal mein Allah taalaa, uskey Rasool aur aakhirat hi ki talabgar hun, phir deegar azwaje-mutahrat ney bhi isi tarah kaha jis tarah mainey kaha tha. to jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon sey ye kuch kaha aur unhoney aap hi ko ikhtiyar kya to ye Talaq na bani kyonkey unhoney (bajaey Talaq key) aap ko ikhtiyar kya."
3470,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab ye aayat utri : « { وَاِنْ کُنْتُنَّ تُرِدْنَ اللّٰہَ وَرَسُوْلَہُ }  agar tum Allah taalaa, uskey Rasool aur aakhirat ko pasand karti ho. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : aey Aaisha! main tujh sey eik baat zikr karney laga hun. tujhey jawab mein jaldi ki koi zarurat nahin yahan tak ke to apney waliden sey bhi mashwara kar ley. aap jantey they ke Allah ki qasam! merey waliden mujhey kabhi bhi aap sey judai ka mashwara nahin dey saktey. phir aap ney mujh par ye aayat tilawat farmaai : { یٰآیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ قُلْ لِّاَزْوَاجِکَ اِنْ کُنْتُنَّ … }  aey Nabi ! apni biwiyon sey keh dijiye : agar tum duniya ki zindagi aur zeb o zeenat chahti ho to. mainey fauran kaha : kya main is barey mein apney waliden sey mashwara lun? main to (har haal mein) Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool hi ki talabgar hun. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke ye, yani hadees Maamar an Zohri, an Urwa, an Aaisha ghalati hai. aur pehli, yani hadees Yunus o Musa bin Ali an ibne-Shahab, an abi Salma an Aaisha durust hai. « wallahu-aalam » ."
3471,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum ko ikhtiyar diya tha aur hamney aap hi ko pasand kya tha to kya ye Talaq ban gaee?
3472,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon ko ikhtiyar diya tha lekin ye Talaq nahin bana.
3473,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon ko ikhtiyar diya tha lekin ye ikhtiyar Talaq nahin bana.
3474,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni azwaje-mutahrat ko Talaq ka ikhtiyar diya tha to kya ye Talaq bin gaya? ( jab ke unhoney aap ko ikhtiyar kya tha).
3475,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Talaq leney ka ikhtiyar diya tha. hum sab ney (Talaq key bajaey) aap ko pasand kya. chunanche aap ney us amal ko hamarey khilaf Talaq shumar nahin farmaya.
3476,"Hazrat Qasim bin Muhammad sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas eik ghulam aur eik londi they ( jo aapas mein miyan biwi they ). Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : mainey unhen azad karney ka irada kya. mainey ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : ghulam ko pehley azad karna, londi ko baad mein."
3477,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein teen sharae ehkam jari huye : eik ye ke wo azad hui to usey apney khawind ki baabat ikhtiyar diya gaya. doosra ye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haqe-wala usey hasil hoga jo azad kerey. teesra ye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to handiya mein gosht pak raha tha lekin aap ko roti key sath ghar wala salan diya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey to handiya mein gosht pakta huwa dekha tha. ghar walon ney kaha : ji haan! aey Allah key Rasool! lekin ye to wo gosht tha jo Barira par sadqa kya gaya tha aur aap sadqa nahin khatey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye uskey liye sadqa tha (lekin jab us ney hamen tohfa bhej diya to ye) hamarey liye hadiya hai.
3478,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein teen aham faisley huye : uskey malikon ney usey bechney ka irada kya lekin wala ki shart lagai. mainey ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : usey kharid ley aur azad kar dey. wala to usi key liye hai jo azad kerey. wo azad hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey ikhtiyar diya. chunanche us ney (khawind key bajaey ) apney aap ko pasand kya. is par sadqa kya jata tha to wo is mein sey hamen tohfey key taur par bhej deti thi. mainey ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : khaao ye uskey liye sadqa hai aur hamarey liye tohfa .
3479,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Barira ko kharid lekin uskey malikon ney wala ki shart laga li. mainey ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : to usey azad kar dey. wala usi shakhs key liye hai jo paisey dey kar khareedta hai. chunanche mainey usey azad kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey bulaya aur usey apney khawind (key sath rehney ya na rehney) ki baabat ikhtiyar diya. wo kehney lagi : wo mujhey bahut badi dolat dey tab bhi main uskey nikah mein rehney key liye tayyar nahin, chunanche us ney apni alehdgi ko pasand kar liya aur us ka khawind azad tha."
3480,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Barira ko kharidney ka irada kya magar uskey malikon ney wala ki shart laga li. mainey ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : to kharid kar azad kar dey. wala to usi key liye hai jo azad karta hai. neez aap key paas gosht laya gaya aur bataya gaya ke ye gosht Barira par sadqa kya gaya tha (us ney hamen bheja hai.) aap ney farmaya : wo uskey liye sadqa tha, hamarey liye tohfa hai. neez Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey ikhtiyar diya jabke uska khawind azad tha."
3481,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Barira ney apney malikon sey apni azadi ka muahida no oqiye ki shart par kya tha. har saal eik auqiya ada karna tha. chunaanche wo merey paas madad leney key liye aai to mainey kaha : agar terey Malik chahen to main unhen yak musht sari raqam deney (aur tujhey khareedney) ko tayyar hun. (phir main tujhey azad kar dungi) aur wala merey liye hogi. Barira apney malikon key paas gaee aur un sey uskey mutalliq baat cheet ki. unhoney (is tarah bechney sey) inkar kar diya illa ye ke wala in ko miley. us ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko aa kar bata diya. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi aa gaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Allah ki qasam! is tarah to main nahin kharidungi. illa ye ke wala mujhey miley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya baat hai? mainey guzarish ki : aey Allah key Rasool! Barira merey paas apni kitaabat key silsiley mein taawun key liye aai thi. mainey kaha : is tarah to nahin lekin agar wo chahen to main puri raqam yakmusht dey kar tujhey kharid kar azad kar deti hun, aur wala mujhey miley. us ney ye baat apney malikon sey kahi to unhoney is tarah bechney sey inkar kar diya, illa ye ke wala in ko miley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to usey kharid ley (aur azad kar dey ) unkey liye wala ki shart maan ley. beshak wala to usi key liye hai jo azad kerey. phir aap ney ( masjid mein) khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmaya : aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd o sanaa farmaai, phir aap ney farmaya : un logon ka kya haal hai jo aisi shartein lagatey hain jin ka jawaz Allah ki kitab mein nahin. wo kehtey hain : falan ghulam ko azad to kar magar wala merey liye hogi. Allah Taala ki kitab (ka hukm) ziyada moatabar hai aur Allah Taala ki jayez karda shart hi mazbut hai aur jis shart ka jawaz Allah Taala ki kitab mein na ho wo ghair moatabar hai, chahey so dafa lagai jaey. phir (azadi key baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Barira ko uskey khawind ki baabat ikhtiyar dey diya aur wo ghulam tha. chunanche Barira ney apney aap ko pasand kya (yani nikah khatam kar liya). Hazrat Urwa ney farmaya : agar uska khawind azad hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey ikhtiyar na detey."
3482,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Barira ka khawind ghulam tha.
3483,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kuch ansariyon sey Barira ko kharid to unhoney wala ki shart lagai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wala to usi key liye hai jo ( azadi ka) ehsan kerey. neez Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey (khawind key barey mein) ikhtiyar diya aur us ka khawind ghulam tha. ( isi tarah ) Barira ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein kuch gosht bheja. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tum hamarey liye bhi kuch gosht rakh letey (to kya hi achcha hota). Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : ye gosht Barira par sadqa kya gaya tha. aap ney farmaya : wo uskey liye sadqa tha, hamarey liye hadiya hai."
3484,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Hazrat Barira key barey mein puchha. mera irada tha ke main usey kharid lun (aur azad kar dun ) lekin uskey malikon ney wala ki shart laga di. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kharid ley, wala to usi key liye hai jo azad kerey. farmaya : ( usi tarah) Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko ikhtiyar diya gaya jabke unka khawind ghulam tha. phir baad mein mein raawi hadees ( Abdur-Rehman ) ney kaha : main nahin janta (ke wo ghulam tha ya azad ). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas kuch gosht laya gaya. ghar walon ney kaha ye Barira par sadqa kya gaya tha. aap ney farmaya : ye uskey liye sadqa tha aur hamarey liye tohfa hai."
3485,"Hazrat Abu Zuha key shagirdon ney unkey paas mahiney key barey mein behes ki. kisi ney kaha : ( mahina ) tees din ka hota hai, kisi ney kaha : untees din ka hota hai. Hazrat Abu Zuha kehney lagey : hamen Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke eik din subh hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaje-mutahrat ro rahi thin. har zauja mutahra key paas unkey ghar waley bethey they. mein masjid mein dakhil huwa to wo logon sey bhari hui thi. itney mein Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aa gaey. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas janey key liye ooper chadhey kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney chaubaarey mein they. unhoney aap ko salam kya lekin kisi ney jawab na diya, phir salam kaha lekin kisi ney jawab na diya. phir salam kaha, phir kisi ney jawab na diya. wo wapis lot aaye to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen pukara , chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur arz kya : aap ney apni biwiyon ko Talaq dey di hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin lekin mainey eik mahina door rehney ki qism kha li hai. aap untees din isi tarah rahey. phir utrey aur apni biwiyon key yahan tashrif ley gaey."
3486,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon sey eik maah tak alag rehney ki qism kha li aur apney chaubaarey mein ja thehrey. chunanche aap untis raaten thehrey rahey. phir aap utar aaye. aap sey kaha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool! kya aap ney eik maah ki qism nahin khai thi? aap ney farmaya : mahina untis ka bhi hota hai.
3487,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya jabke us ney apni biwi sey zihar kar rakha tha, phir wo us sey jima kar betha. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey apni biwi sey zihar kar rakha tha lekin kaffara deney sey qabl jima kar betha hun. aap ney farmaya : Allah tujh par reham farmaai ! tujhey kis chiz ney is kaam par majbur kya tha. us ney kaha : mainey chaand ki chaandni mein uski paazeb dekhi (to zabt na kar saka ). aap ney farmaya : ab uskey qarib na jana yahan tak ke to wo kaam karey jo Allah Taala ney karney ka hukm diya hai."
3488,Hazrat ikrima sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi sey zihar kya lekin kaffara deney sey pehley hi jima kar liya. us ney ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney usey farmaya : tujhey kis chiz ney is kaam par majbur kya ? wo kehney laga : Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala aap par rahmatein farmaaey ! mainey chaand ki chaandni mein uski paazeb ya pindliyan dekhin (aur zabt na kar saka) aap ney farmaya : ab us sey door rehna yahan tak ke to wo kaam karey jiska Allah Taala ney hukm diya hai.
3489,"Hazrat ikrima sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Nabi ! mainey apni biwi sey zihar kya tha, phir kaffara ada karney sey pehley mainey us sey jima kar liya. aap ney farmaya : tujhey kis chiz ney aisa karney par majbur kya ? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! mainey chaandni mein uski pindliyon ki safedi dekhi. aap ney farmaya : ab alehda rehna yahan tak ke to apney zimmey wajib kaffara ada kerey. Is-haq ney apni hadees mein ye alfaz bayan kiye hain : ab us sey alehda rehna yahan tak ke to apney zimmey wajib kaffara ada kerey. ye alfaz ustaad Muhammad abdul-Aala key hain. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke mazkura baala dono riwaayatein musnad key bajaey mursal hi sahih hain. « wallahu-aalam » ."
3490,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke tareef us Allah ki hai jiski samaat ney tamam aawaazon ko gher rakha hai. Hazrat khaula (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas apney khawind ki shikayat karney ayen (aur wo is qadr aahista bol rahi thin ke) unki sab baaten main bhi nahin sun rahi thi ke Allah Taala ney wahi utaar di : « { قَدْ سَمِعَ اللّٰہُ قَوْلَ الَّتِیْ … }  Allah Taala ney us aurat ki baat sun li jo tum sey apney khawind key barey mein behes kar rahi thi aur wo Allah Taala sey uski shikayat kar rahi thi, aur Allah Taala tum dono ki baaten sun raha tha … ."
3491,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney aap ko khaawindon sey chudaney wali Talaq ka mutalba karney wali aurten munafiq hain. Hasan ( Basri ) kehtey hain : mainey is hadees ko Abu-Hurera key ilawa kisi sey nahin suna. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) farmatey hain : Hasan ( Basri ) ney Abu-Hurera sey kuch bhi nahin suna.
3492,". Hazrat Habiba bint Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas key nikah thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subh ki namaz key liye nikley to Habiba bint Sahal ko andherey mein apney darwazey key paas khadey paya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kon hai. ? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main Habiba bint Sahal hun. aap ney farmaya : tum kaisey ? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main nahin aur Sabit bin Qais nahin. apney shohar key mutalliq kaha. ( matlab ye tha ke ab mein aur mera khawind Sabit bin Qais ikhattey nahin reh saktey. ) jab Hazrat Sabit bin Qais aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey kaha : ye Habiba bint Sahal ( aai ) hai aur Allah Taala ko jo kuch manzoor tha us ney ( mujh sey) bayan kya. Habiba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! unhoney jo kuch ( haq mehar ) mujhey diya tha, merey paas mojud hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Sabit sey kaha : apna maal us sey wapis ley ley. chunanche unhoney wapis ley liya aur Habiba apney ghar walon key yahan ( meykey mein) beth rahi."
3493,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sabit bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayen aur kehney lagin : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney khawind Sabit bin Qais par Deen ya khalq key lihaz sey koi aeb nahin lagaati lekin main musalman ho kar kufr key kaam karna napasand karti hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to uska diya huwa baagh usey wapis kar degi? unhoney kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( Sabit bin Qais sey) farmaya : baagh wapis ley lo aur usey Talaq dey do.
3494,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kehney laga : meri biwi kisi chhuney waley ka haath nahin rokti. aap ney farmaya : agar to chahey to usey Talaq dey dey. wo kehney laga : mujhey khatra hai ke mera dil us ka peecha nahin chodega. aap ney farmaya : phir us sey faeyda uthata reh.
3495,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey nikah main eik aurat hai jo kisi chhed chhaad karney waley key haath ko nahin rokti. aap ney farmaya : usey Talaq dey do. wo kehney laga : main us sey judai bardasht nahin kar sakta. aap ney farmaya : phir rakhey rakh. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) farmatey hain : ye khata hai aur sahih ye hai ke ye hadees mursal hai.
3496,"Hazrat Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Banu Ajlan key eik shakhs Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Aasim ! batao agar eik aadmi apni biwi key sath kisi aadmi ko dekh ley to kya wo usey qatl kar dey ? ke phir tum usey qatl kar dogey. aakhir wo kya karey ? aey Aasim ! aap ye masla merey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochen . Hazrat Aasim ney is barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is qism key sawalat poochhney ko pasand na farmaya, balke mazammat ki. Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) dobara Hazrat Aasim key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : Aasim ! aap ney kya kya ? Aasim ney kaha : tum merey paas koi achcha sawal nahin laye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is qism key sawalaat ko napasand farmaya hai balke mazammat farmaai hai. Uwemir kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! main to zarur uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochhunga. chunanche wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur aap sey puchha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney teri biwi aur terey barey mein wahi nazil farma di hai. ja, usey ley aa. Hazrat Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main logon key sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha tha ke Uwemir apni biwi ko ley kar aaye, phir dono ney liaan kya. Uwemir kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar ab bhi mainey usey apney nikah mein rakha to phir to (goya) mainey is par jhoot bola hai. chunanche unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm deney sey qabl hi usey Talaq dey di, phir ye liaan karney walon key liye sharae tariqa bin gaya (ke unkey darmiyan hatmi judai ho jaeygi )."
3497,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Uwemir) Ajlani aur uski biwi key darmiyan liaan karwaya jabke wo ( biwi ) hamila thi.
3498,"Hazrat Hisham sey us aadmi key barey mein puchha gaya jo apni biwi par zina ka ilzam lagata hai, to unhoney Hazrat Muhammad ( bin Sirin ) sey bayan kya ke unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey us barey mein puchha aur mujhey yaqin tha ke unkey paas uski baabat ilm hoga. wo farmaney lagey ke Hazrat Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni biwi par Sharik bin Sehma key sath zina ka ilzam lagaya. aur ye Hazrat Baraa bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key Akhyafi (maa sharik) bhai they aur unhoney sab sey pehley liaan kya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khawind biwi key darmiyan liaan karwaya. phir aap ney farmaya : usey ( paida honey waley bachey ko) dekhna. agar us aurat ney usey safed rang wala, sidhey baalon wala aur kharab si aakhon wala jana to wo Hilal bin Umayya hi ka hoga aur agar us ney surmili aakhon wala, ghunghraley baalon wala aur patli pindliyon wala jana to wo Sharik bin Sehma ka hoga. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mujhey batlaya gaya ke us aurat ney bachey ko surmili aakhon wala, ghunghraaley baalon wala aur patli pindliyon wala jana."
3499,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Islam mein sab sey pehla liaan yun huwa ke Hazrat Hilal bin Umayya ney apni biwi par Sharik bin Sehma key sath zina ka ilzam lagaya, chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur aap ko puri baat batai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : chaar gawah laao warna teri pusht par had lagegi. ye baat aap usey bar-bar farma rahey they. Hazrat Hilal ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala janta hai ke main yaqinan sacha hun aur Allah Taala yaqinan aap par wahi nazil farmaeyga jo meri pusht ko had sey bacha legi. abhi wo ye baaten kar hi rahey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par liaan ki aayat utarney lagi : « { وَالَّذِیْنَ یَرْمُوْنَ اَزْوَاجَھُمْ … }  aur jo log apni biwiyon par ilzam lagaeyn … . aap ney Hilal ko bulaya. unhoney chaar qasmen khaain ke main yaqinan (is ilzam mein) sacha hun aur paanchwen qism ye khai ke agar main jhoota hun to mujh par Allah Taala ki lanat ho. phir aurat ko bulaya gaya. us ney bhi Allah Taala key naam ki chaar qasmen khaain ke ye yaqinan jhoota hai. jab chauthi ya paanchwin qism honey lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey rok lo kyonkey ye ( qism jahannam ko) wajib kar degi. wo eik dafa to ruki yahan tak ke hamen zarra bhar shak na raha ke wo gunah ka aetraaf keregi, lekin phir wo kehney lagi : main rehti duniya tak apni qom ko ruswa nahin karungi. aakhir us ney qism kha li. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dhiyan rakhna agar to usney safed rang ka, sidhey baalon wala aur kharab aakhon wala bacha jana, phir to wo Hilal bin Umayya hi ka hoga aur agar us ney gandumi rang ka, ghunghraaley baalon wala, darmiyaney qad ka aur patli pindliyon wala bacha jana to wo Sharik bin Sehma ka hoga. us aurat ney baad mein gandumi rang ka, ghunghraaley baalon wala, darmiyaney qad ka aur patli pindliyon wala bacha jana to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar Allah Taala ki kitab mein hukm likha na ja chuka hota to duniya dekhti, main us sey kya sulook karta. Shekh (Imam Nasai) bayan kartey hain ke kharab aakhon waley sey murad ye hai ke aakhon key baal lambey hon, aankhen puri khulti na hon aur na wo moti hon. « wallah Subhanahu w taala aalim » ."
3500,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas liaan ka tazkira huwa to Hazrat Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ney is barey mein koi baat kahi. jab wo (ghar) wapis gaey to unki qom ka eik aadmi unkey paas aa kar shikayat karney laga ke mainey apni biwi key sath eik aadmi paya hai. Hazrat Aasim kehney lagey : main is musibat mein apney us qol ki wajeh sey mubtala huwa hun. wo us shakhs ko ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaey aur aap ko us shakhs key barey mein bataya jiskey sath us ney apni biwi ko dekha tha. wo shakhs (shikayat kuninda) zard rang ka, thodey gosht wala, safed baalon wala tha. aur jis shakhs key barey mein us ka daawa tha ke usey us ney apni biwi key sath paya hai, wo shakhs gandumi rang ka, moti pindliyon wala aur ziyada gosht wala tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! soorate-haal wazeh farma dena. chunanche us aurat ney us shakhs key mushabeh bacha jana jiskey barey mein uskey khawind ney kaha tha ke mainey usey apni biwi key sath ( haalate-zina mein) dekha hai. khair ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey darmiyan liaan karwa diya tha. majlis mein mojud eik shakhs ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas sey kaha : kya ye wohi aurat thi jis key mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : agar main kisi ko gawahon key baghair rajm karta to us aurat ko karta. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : nahin, wo eik dusri aurat thi jo musalman honey key bawajud bad-kari mein mashhoor thi (magar gawah nahin miltey they )."
3501,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas liaan ka zikr huwa to Hazrat Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ney koi baat kahi, phir ( ghar ) wapis gaey to un ki qom ka eik aadmi unhen mila. us ney kaha ke us ney apni biwi key sath eik aadmi ko ( haalat zina mein) dekha hai. Hazrat Aasim usey ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaey to us shakhs ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us aadmi ka zikr kya jisey us ney apni biwi key sath ( haalate-zina mein) dekha tha. (shikayat karneywala) shakhs zard rang ka, thodey gosht wala aur sidhey baalon wala tha. aur jis shakhs key barey mein usney daawa kya tha ke usey apni biwi key sath dekha hai, wo gandumi rang ka, moti pindliyon wala, ziyada gosht wala aur sakht ghunghraaley baalon wala tha. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! soorate-haal wazeh farma. phir us aurat ney us aadmi key mushabeh bacha jana jis key barey mein uskey khawind ney kaha tha ke mainey usey apni biwi key sath (qabile-aetraz haalat mein) paya hai. (us sey pehley) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) un mein liaan karwa chukey they. majlis mein mojud eik shakhs ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya yehi wo aurat thi jis key barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha ke agar main kisi ko baghair gawahon key rajm karta to usey karta? Hazrat ibne-Abbas ney farmaya : nahin, wo eik aur aurat thi jo musalman honey key bawajud bad-kari mein maroof thi (magar gawah nahin miltey they )."
3502,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jab liaan karney walon ko liaan ka hukm diya to eik aadmi sey farmaya ke paanchwin qism key waqt uskey munh par haath rakh dena aur farmaya : ye (azab ko) wajib kar degi.
3503,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke mujh sey Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key daur khilaafat mein liaan karney walon key barey mein puchha gaya ke kya un mein tafriq kar di jaeygi? meri samajh mein kuch na aaya ke kya kahun. main usi waqt apni jagah sey uth kar Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar ki taraf chal pada. mainey arz kya : aey abu Abdur-Rehman! kya liaan karney waley khawind biwi mein mustaqil judai kar di jaeygi? aap kehney lagey : zarur. subhan Allah! (yani tajjub hai ke tujhey is mashhoor hukm ka ilm nahin. ) sab sey pehley jis shakhs ney liaan key barey mein puchha tha, wo falan bin falan tha. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! farmaiye eik aadmi apni biwi ko zina ki haalat mein dekhta hai, ab agar wo shor machata hai to ye bhi bahut be Izzati ki baat hai, aur agar wo chup rehta hai to aisi baat par chup rehna bhi bahut mushkil hai. aap ney usey koi jawab na diya. uskey kuch din baad wo phir aaya aur kehney laga : jo masla mainey aap sey puchha tha, mein waqiatan is mein mubtala hun, phir Allah Taala ney Sura Noor mein ye aayaat utaar din : « { وَالَّذِیْنَ یَرْمُوْنَ اَزْوَاجَھُمْ … }  wo log jo apni biwiyon par zina ka ilzam laga den … aurat paanchwin qism ye khaye ke agar mera khawind sacha hai to mujh par Allah Taala ka ghazab nazil ho. aap ney pehley aadmi ko bulaya. usey waaz o nasihat ki aur usey bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat key azab sey halka hai. wo kehney laga : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya hai ! mainey (zarra bhar) jhoot nahin bola, phir aap ney aurat ko bulaya. usey bhi waaz o nasihat farmaai. wo bhi kehney lagi : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya hai! yaqinan wo jhoota hai. aap ney pehley aadmi sey qasmen lin. us ney Allah key naam ki chaar qasmen khaain ke yaqinan main sacha hun aur paanchwin qism ye khai ke agar main jhoota hun to mujh par Allah Taala ki lanat ho. phir dusrey number par aap ney aurat sey qasmen lin. us ney bhi Allah Taala key naam ki chaar qasmen khaeyn ke yaqinan ye jhoota hai aur paanchwin qism ye khai ke agar ye sacha ho to mujh par Allah Taala ka ghazab nazil ho. uskey baad aap ney un mein mustaqil judai dal di."
3504,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Musab ney liaan karney walon mein tafriq na ki. mainey ye baat Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey zikr ki to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney to Banu Ajlan key liaan karney waley khawind biwi mein tafriq kar di thi.
3505,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey marwi hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : eik aadmi apni biwi par zina ka ilzam laga dey (aur un mein liaan ho jaey to phir kya hoga ?) unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Banu Ajlan key liaan karney waley khawind biwi key darmiyan judai dal di thi. aur aap ney ( baad mein) farmaya tha : Allah Taala janta hai ke tum mein sey eik to zarur jhoota hai. kya tum mein sey koi tauba karta hai? aap ney teen dafa farmaya : unhoney inkar kya to aap ney un mein judai dal di. wo aadmi kehney laga : mera maal ? aap ney farmaya : tujhey koi maal nahin milega. agar to sacha hai to tu ney us sey jima waghera bhi to kiye hain. aur agar to jhoota hai to phir to tujhey maal mil hi nahin sakta.
3506,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey liaan karney waley khawind biwi key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney liaan karney waley khawind biwi sey farmaya tha : ab tumhara hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. tum mein sey eik to (zarur) jhoota hai. ab to uskey sath nahin reh sakta. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool! mera maal? aap ney farmaya : tujhey koi maal nahin milega. agar to sacha hai to us maal key iwaz to usey istimal bhi to kar chuka hai aur agar to jhoota hai to phir tujhey maal sey kya wasta?
3507,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik khawind biwi mein liaan karwaya, phir unhen juda kar diya aur bacha maa ko dey diya."
3508,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Banu Fazara mein sey eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kaha : meri biwi ney siyah bacha jana hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya terey paas oont hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : unkey rang kaisey hain? us ney kaha : surkh . aap ney farmaya : kya un mein koi khakastri rang ka bhi hai? us ney kaha : ji han, un mein khakastri bhi hain. aap ney farmaya : kya khayal hai wo kidhar sey aa gaey? wo kehney laga : ho sakta hai kisi jaddi rag ka asar ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is bachey mein bhi kisi jaddi rag ka asar ho sakta hai."
3509,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke banu-Fazara mein sey eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar kehney laga : meri biwi ney siyah bacha jana hai. us ka maqsad ye tha ke wo mera nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya terey paas oont hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : kis rang key hain? us ney kaha : surkh . farmaya : kya un mein koi khakastri bhi hai? us ney kaha : ji kaee khakastri hain. aap ney farmaya : to usey to kya samajhta hai? wo kehney laga : kisi jaddi rag ka asar ho sakta hai. aap ney farmaya is bachey mein bhi kisi jaddi rag ka asar ho sakta hai. aap ney usey bachey ki nafi ki ijazat nahin di.
3510,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik dafa hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key yahan hazir they ke eik aadmi khada ho kar kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey ghar siyah rang ka ladka paida huwa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye kaisey ho gaya? us ney kaha : mujhey to koi pata nahin. aap ney farmaya : terey paas oont hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : unka rang kya hai? us ney kaha : surkh. aap ney farmaya : kya un mein koi khakastri oont bhi hai? us ney kaha : ji! bahut sey oont khakastri hain. aap ney farmaya : ye kaisey huwa? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! main haqiqat to nahin janta illa ye ke kisi rag ki kashish ho. aap ney farmaya is bachey mein bhi kisi rag ki kashish ho sakti hai. is bina par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye wazeh faisla farmaya : kisi aadmi ko us bachey ki nafi ki ijazat nahin jo uskey bistar par paida huwa ho, illa ye ke wo daawey karey ke mainey apni biwi ko zina ki haalat mein dekha hai."
3511,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna, jis waqt liaan ki aayat utri thi : jo aurat kisi qom mein aisey bachey ko dakhil kar dey jo un mein sey nahin to us ka Allah Taala sey koi talluq nahin. aur Allah Taala usey jannat mein dakhil nahin farmaeyga. aur jo aadmi apney bachey ka (zid sey ya shak o shubha sey) inkar kar dey jab ke bacha usey (piyaar sey) dekh raha ho, Allah Taala us sey munh mod lega. aur qiyamat key din usey agley pichley sab logon key samney zaleel farmaeyga ."
3512,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bacha bistar key Malik ka hoga aur zaani key liye pathar hain.
3513,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bacha bistar waley ka hai aur zaani key liye pathar hain.
3514,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Saad bin abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abd bin Zamaa eik ladkey key barey mein jhagad padey. Hazrat Saad ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye merey bhai Utba bin abu Waqas ka beta hai. us ney mujhey wasiyat ki thi ke ye mera beta hai. aap zara uski shakal o Shabahat par ghor farmaeyn. Abd bin Zamaa kehney laga : ye mera bhai hai. merey baap key yahan uski londi sey paida huwa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski shakal o shabahat ko dekha to wo wazeh taur par Utba key mushabeh tha. chunanche aap ney farmaya : aey abd ! ye tera bhai hi hai kyonkey bacha ghar waley ka hota hai aur zaani ko to pathar padtey hain. aey sauda bint Zamaa! to us sey parda kya kar. uskey baad us ney kabhi Hazrat sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko nahin dekha.
3515,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Zamaa ki eik londi thi jis sey wo jima kya karta tha. lekin wo eik aur shakhs key barey mein samajhta tha ke wo bhi us sey zina karta hai. baad mein us londi ney us shakhs key mushabeh bacha jana jis key barey mein us ka ye khayal tha. khair ! Zamaa faut huwa to wo hamila thi. Hazrat sauda ney us baat ka zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bacha to ghar waley ki taraf hi mansub hoga lekin to us sey parda kya kar kyonkey haqeeqatan wo tera bhai nahin.
3516,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bacha ghar waley ka hota hai aur zaani key liye pathar hain (ya mehrumi hai). abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood sey nahin aati. (kisi raawi ki ghalati hai). « wallahu-aalam » .
3517,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abd bin Zamaa, Zamaa key eik betey key barey mein jhagad padey. Hazrat Saad ney kaha ke mujhey merey bhai Utba ney wasiyat ki thi ke to jab bhi Makka jaey to Zamaa ki londi sey paida honey waley bachey ko talash kar key pakad lena kyonkey wo mera beta hai. Abd bin Zamaa ney kaha : wo merey baap ki londi ka beta hai. merey baap key bistar par paida huwa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Utba key sath uski wazeh mushaabihat mehsus farmaai magar aap ney farmaya : bacha ghar waley hi ka hota hai lekin sauda ! to us sey parda kya kar."
3518,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas Yamen mein teen aadmi laye gaey jinhoney eik aurat key sath eik tuhur mein jima kya tha. aap ney un mein sey do sey puchha : kya tum us ( teesrey ) key liye bachey ka iqrar kartey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin, phir dusrey do sey puchha : tum us teesrey key liye ye bacha taslim kartey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin. aakhir aap ney un mein qura dala aur bacha usey dey diya jis key naam qura nikla tha. aur is par us bachey ki do tihai diyat dal di. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki gaee to aap hansney lagey yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin"
3519,Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik dafa hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir they ke aap key paas Yamen sey eik aadmi aaya. wo aap ko wahan ki baaten bayan karney laga. Hazrat Ali bhi un dino Yamen mein they. wo shakhs kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas teen aadmi aaye jin ka eik bachey key barey mein jhagda tha. un teeno ney eik tuhur main eik aurat sey jima kya tha. aur mazkura baala ki maanind sari hadees bayan ki.
3520,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas mojud tha. un dino Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen mein they. aap key paas eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : mainey dekha ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas teen aadmiyon ka muqadma aaya jinhoney eik aurat key bachey key barey mein daawa kya tha. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney un mein sey eik sey kaha : kya to ye bacha us ko deta hai? us ney inkar kya, phir dusrey sey kaha : to ye bacha us ko deta hai? us ney bhi inkar kya, phir teesrey sey kaha : to ye bacha us ko deta hai? us ney bhi inkar kya. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tum jhagdalu shareek ho. main tum mein qura dalunga. jis key haq mein qura nikal aaya, bacha usey mil jaeyga. albatta usey do tihai diyat ada karna hogi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye sun kar hansney lagey yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin."
3521,Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen par haakim bana kar bheja . unkey paas eik bacha laya gaya jis mein teen aadmiyon ka jhagda tha. aur mazkura baala ki maanind sari hadees bayan ki. Salma bin kuheil ney un ki mukhalifat ki hai.
3522,"Hazrat abu-Khaleel ya ibne-abu-Khaleel sey manqul hai ke teen aadmi eik aurat key tuhur mein shareek huye. baqi hadees isi tarah zikr ki, neez Salma bin kuheil ney ( apni riwayat mein) Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin kya aur na riwayat ko marfooa hi bayan kya hai. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) farmatey hain ke yehi ( Salma bin kuheil ki riwayat ) durust hai. « wallah Subhanahu w taala aalam» ."
3523,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik dafa merey paas khush khush tashrif laye. aap key chehra mubarak ki dhaariyan chamak rahi thin. aap ney farmaya : ( Aaisha ! ) tujhey pata chala ke Mujazzaz ney Zaid bin Harisa aur Usama ko (letey huye) dekha to kaha : ye paaun eik dusrey ( baap betey ) hi key ( malum hotey ) hain.
3524,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) badey khush khush merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaney lagey : Aaisha ! tujhey ilm nahin ke abhi Mujazzaz Mudliji merey paas aaya tha jab ke Usama bin Zaid merey qarib ( leta huwa ) tha. us ney Usama aur Zaid dono ko dekha. dono key ooper chadar thi aur unhoney apney chehrey dhanp rakhey they, albatta unkey paaun nangey they, chunanche (ye dekh kar) wo kehney laga : ye paaun to eik dusrey (baap betay) key ( malum hotey ) hain."
3525,"Hazrat abdul-hameed bin Salma Ansari key dada mohtaram sey riwayat hai ke main musalman ho gaya lekin meri biwi ney Islam laney sey inkar kar diya. hamara eik chhota bacha aaya jo abhi baligh nahin huwa tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney baap ko eik taraf bitha liya aur maa ko dusri taraf, phir aap ney bachey ko ikhtiyar diya aur dua farmaai : ya Allah ! usey hidayat dey. chunanche wo bacha ( Allah ki tofiq sey) baap ki taraf chala gaya."
3526,"Hazrat Abu-Memuna bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key paas tha to unhoney farmaya : eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kehney lagi : aap par merey maa baap fidaa hon! mera (sabiqa) khawind merey betey ko ley jana chahta hai jab ke wo mujhey bahut nafa deta hai, maslan Abi-anba kuney sey mujhey pani la kar dey deta hai. itney mein us ka khawind bhi aa gaya aur kehney laga : merey betey key barey mein kon mujh sey jhagda kar sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : aey ladkey ! ye tera baap hai aur ye teri maa, jis ka chahey haath pakad ley. us ney apni walida ka haath pakad liya aur wo usey ley kar chali gaee."
3527,"Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni biwi ko maara aur uska haath tod diya. uska naam Jamila bint Abdullah bin Ubai tha. us ka bhai ye shikayat ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat sabit ko pegham bhej kar bulaya aur ( tehqiq key baad ) farmaya : tu ney jo kuch usey diya hai, wapis ley ley aur usey chhod dey. us ney kaha : theek hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat jameela ko hukm diya ke wo eik haiz tak intizar karey aur meykey chali jaey."
3528,"Hazrat Ubada bin waleed bin Ubada bin Saamit sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Rabeea bint muawwiz (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha ke mujhey apna waqia bayan kijiye. wo kehney lagi ke mainey apney khawind sey khula liya, phir main Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key paas hazir hui aur aap sey puchha : mujh par kitni iddat wajib hai? unhoney farmaya : tujh par koi iddat wajib nahin magar ye ke terey khawind ney tujh sey us tuhur mein jima kya ho to phir to eik haiz intizar kar. unhoney farmaya : is silsiley mein mainey Maryam Maghaliya ki baabat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key faisley ki perwi ki hai. wo Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas key nikah mein thi aur unhoney unsey khula le liya tha."
3529,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney (naskh key dalaeyl zikr kartey huye) ye aayaat padhein : (مَا نَنْسْخْ مِنْ اٰیۃٍ … اَوْ مِثْلِھَا) jo aayat hum mansookh kar den ya bhula den, hum us sey behtar aayat latey hain ya us jaisi. aur farmaya : « { وَاِذَا بَدَّلْنَآ اٰیَۃً … بِمَا یُنَزِّلُ }  jab hum eik aayat ki jagah dusri aayat ley aatey hain, aur Allah Taala apni utaari hui aayaat ko khub janta hai. aur farmaya : « { یَمْحُو اللہُ مَایَشَآءُ … أُمُّ الْکِتَابِ }  Allah Taala jo chahey mita deta hai aur jo chahey baqi rakhta hai aur Allah Taala hi key paas asal kitab hai. Quran Majeed mein sab sey pehley qibla mansookh huwa. isi tarah Allah Taala ney farmaya : « { وَالْمُطَلَّقٰتُ یَتَرَبَّصْنَ بِاَنْفُسِھِنَّ ثَلٰثَۃَ قُرُوْءٍ }  Talaq shuda aurten teen haiz tak apney aap ko (naya nikah karney sey) rok rakhen. phir farmaya : { وَالّٰئِی یَئِسْنَ مِنَ الْمَحِیْضِ … ثَلٰثَۃُ اَشْھُرٍ }  wo aurten jo haiz sey na-umeed ho chuki hain, agar tumhen shak ho to un ki iddat teen mahiney hai. (us aayat key zariey sey) pehli aayat mein sey kuch hissa mansookh kar diya gaya. phir Allah Taala ney farmaya : { ثُمَّ طَلَّقْتُمُوْھُنَّ مِنْ قَبْلِ اَنْ تَمَسُّوْھُنَّ … تَعْتَدِوْنَھَا }  agar tum aurton ko jima sey pehley Talaq do to un par koi iddat nahin jisey tum shumar karo."
3530,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo aurat Allah Taala aur aakhirat par eman rakhti ho, uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din sey zayed sog kerey. albatta khawind par chaar maah das din sog kerey."
3531,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik aurat key barey mein puchha gaya jis ka khawind faut ho chuka tha aur uski aakhon key zaya honey ka khatra tha, kya wo surma dal sakti hai? aap ney farmaya : (door jahiliyat mein) eik aurat ko apney ghar main eik saal tak bad-tareen taat mein rehna padta tha, phir wo nikalti thi. wo kya ab wo chaar mahiney das din tak intizar nahin kar sakti?"
3532,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur kehney lagi : meri beti ka khawind faut ho gaya hai. mujhey uski aankh kharab honey ka khadsha hai, to kya main usey surma dal dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (us sey pehley jahiliyat mein) aurat ko eik saal tak ghar mein ( band ) rehna padta tha jab ke ab to sirf chaar maah das din hain. jab saal pura hota tha to wo nikalti thi aur apney peechey oont ki mengni phenka karti thi."
3533,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Hafsa binte-Umar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat Allah Taala aur aakhirat par yaqin rakhti hai uskey liye jayez nahin ke kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey. ilawa khawind key ke is par usey chaar mahiney das din sog karna hoga.
3534,Hazrat Umme-Salma aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik aur zauja mohtarma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat Allah Taala aur youm aakhirat par yaqin rakhti hai uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey. ilawa khawind key ke is par wo chaar maah das din tak sog keregi .
3535,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sabiqa hadees ki tarah hi riwayat bayan farmati hain.
3536,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke sabeeaa Aslamiya ka uskey khawind ki wafat sey chand raaten baad bacha paida ho gaya, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur nikah ki ijazat talab ki. chunanche aap ney usey ijazat dey di aur us ney nikah kar liya."
3537,Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Sabiaa (Raziallahu anha) ko ijazat di thi ke jab wo nifaas sey pak ho jaey to aagey nikah kar sakti hai.
3538,Hazrat Abu-Sanaabil (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Sabeeaa (Raziallahu anha) ney apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey teyis ya pachchees raaton key baad bachcha jan diya. jab wo nifaas sey pak hui to usney naee shaadi ki khahish ki lekin uski is baat ko bura jana gaya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ye baat zikr ki gaee. aap ney farmaya : usey kya rukawat hai? uski iddat khatam ho chuki hai.
3539,"Hazrat Abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma mein us aurat key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya jis ka khawind faut ho gaya. baad mein us ney bachcha jan diya. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo aagey shaadi kar sakti hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas ney farmaya : nahin, wo baad wali iddat puri karey. phir unhoney Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas (faisley key liye) pegham bheja to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Sabeeaa ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya. us ney wafat sey pandarah din, yani nisf (aadha) mahina baad bachcha jan diya. usey do aadmiyon ney shaadi ka pegham bhej diya. wo un mein sey eik ki taraf maael ho gaee. dusrey shakhs aur uskey sathiyon ney mehsus kiya ke wo apni marzi keregi to wo kehney lagey : teri to iddat puri nahin hui. wo kehti hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaee to aap ney farmaya : teri iddat puri ho chuki hai jis sey chahey nikah kar."
3540,"Hazrat Abu-Salma sey marwi hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey us aurat key barey mein puchha gaya jis ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya ho aur wo hamila ho. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo baad wali iddat puri kerey. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab wo bachcha jan dey to uski iddat puri ho gaee. Abu-Salma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaey aur un sey ye masla puchha to unhoney farmaya : Sabeeaa Aslamiya ney apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey nisf (aadha) maah baad bacha jan diya to do aadmiyon ney usey shaadi ka pegham bheja. un mein sey eik jawan tha, doosra kuchh boodha. wo jawan ki taraf maael hui to wo boodha kehney laga : teri to abhi iddat hi puri nahin hui. asal baat ye thi ke aurat key ghar waley ghaaieb they. usey ummid thi ke agar ghar waley aagey to shaadi key mamley mein usey tarjeeh dengey lekin wo aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunch gaee. aap ney farmaya : teri iddat puri ho chuki hai jis sey pasand karey nikah kar."
3541,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey us aurat key barey mein puchha gaya jo apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat key bees raaten baad bachcha jan dey, kya uskey liye aagey nikah karna durust hai? unhoney farmaya : nahin, balke usey dono (chaar maah das din aur bachcha jan'na) main sey aakhiri iddat puri kerni hogi. mainey kaha : Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : (وَاُولاَتُ الْاَحْماَلِ … حَمْلَھُنَّ),'' hamila aurton ki iddat ye hai ke bachcha jan den.'' aap farmaney lagey : ye Talaq ki surat mein hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main apney bhateejey (Abu-Salma) key sath hun. chunanche Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney ghulam Kureb ko bheja aur farmaya : Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas jaao aur un sey poochho kya is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka koi farman hai? wo gaya to unhoney farmaya : han, Sabeeaa Aslamiya ney apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey bees din baad bachcha jan diya tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey nikah karney ki ijazat dey di. aur Hazrat Abu-Sanaabil ney bhi usey shaadi ka pegham bheja tha."
3542,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), isi ke sath Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ney us aurat ki iddat ka tazkira farmaya jis ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya ho aur wo wafat sey thodey arsey baad bachcha jan dey. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo dono mein sey aakhiri iddat guzaarey. Hazrat Abu-Salma ney farmaya : balke bachcha paida honey sey uski iddat khatam ho jaeygi. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main apney bhateejey key sath hun. phir unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas pegham bheja to unhoney farmaya : Sabeeaa Aslamiya ney apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey thoda arsey baad bachcha jan diya tha, phir us ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney usey nikah ki ijazat marahmat farma di."
3543,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Sabeeaa ney apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey chand din baad bachcha jan diya tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey aagey nikah karney ki ijazat dey di.
3544,Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar sey manqul hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ka us aurat key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya jisey apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey chand din baad bachcha paida ho gaya. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : usey dono mein sey baad wali iddat guzaarni hogi. Hazrat Abu-Salma ney farmaya : jab bachcha paida ho jaey to uski iddat khatam ho jati hai. itney mein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aa gaey. wo farmaney lagey : main apney bhateejey Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ki taeed karta hun. unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas key Mola Kureb ko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas ye masla poochhney key liye bheja. us ney wapis aa kar batlaya ke unhoney farmaya hai : Sabeeaa ney apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat sey chand din baad bachcha jan diya tha aur us ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : teri iddat khatam ho gaee hai.
3545,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke main, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ikhattey bethey they. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : jab koi aurat apney khawind (shohar) ki wafat key baad bachcha jan dey to uski iddat dono mein sey aakhiri hai. Hazrat Abu-Salma ney kaha : hamney Hazrat Kureb ko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas iskey barey mein poochhney key liye bheja. chunanche wo unkey paas sey ho kar hamarey paas ye khabar laye ke Sabeeaa ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya tha aur us ney apney khawind ki wafat key chand din baad bachcha jan diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey nikah karney ki ijazat dey di."
3546,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke qabila Aslam ki eik aurat jis ka naam Sabeeaa tha, wo apney khawind (shohar) key nikah mein thi ke us ka khawind faut ho gaya jab ke wo hamila thi. Hazrat Abu-Sanaabil bin ba'kak (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey shaadi ka pegham bheja lekin us ney un sey nikah karney sey inkar kar diya. chunanche wo kehney lagey : terey liye to abhi nikah karna durust hi nahin yahan tak ke to dono iddaton mein sey aakhiri iddat guzar ley. taqriban bees raaten guzrin to usney bachcha jan diya tha. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai to aap ney farmaya : to nikah kar sakti hai."
3547,Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa main aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas mojud they ke eik aurat aai aur us ney kaha : mera khawind (shohar) faut huwa to main hamila thi. mainey uski wafat key baad chaar maah (das din) purey honey sey pehley hi bachcha jan diya. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke dono muddaton mein sey aakhiri muddat puri kerni hogi. Abu-Salma ney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba mein sey eik shakhs ney mujhey khabar di ke Sabeeaa Aslamiya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kehney lagi : mera khawind faut ho gaya. main hamila thi. mainey chaar maah (das din) sey pehley bachcha jan diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey nikah karney ki ijazat dey di. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main bhi iski taeed karta hun.
3548,Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah bayan kartey hain ke merey walid mohtaram ney Hazrat umr bin Abdullah bin Arqam Zohri ko likha ke wo Sabeeaa binte Haris Aslamiya key paas jaeyn aur un sey unka waqia poochhen ke jab unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha to aap ney unhen kya jawab diya tha. to Hazrat umr bin Abdullah ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Utba ko likha ke Hazrat Sabeeaa ney mujhey bataya hai ke wo Hazrat Saad bin khaula (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thi. wo banu Aamir bin Lavi qabeeley sey talluq rakhtey they. jange-badar mein hazir huye they. Hajjatul-wadaa key doran mein wo faut ho gaey. us waqt wo hamila thi. un ki wafat sey thoda arsey baad us ney bachcha jan diya. jab wo nifaas sey pak hui to usney shaadi ka pegham bhejney walon key liye zeb aur zeenat ki. banu Abduddaar key eik aadmi Abu-Sanaabil bin Ba'kak uskey yahaan aaye to kehney lagey : kya wajeh hai ke tu ney zeenat kar rakhi hai? shayad to aagey nikah karney ka irada rakhti hai. Allah ki qism ! to nikah nahin kar sakti yahan tak ke chaar maah das din guzar jaeyn. Hazrat Sabeeaa ney farmaya : jab unhoney mujhey ye baat kahi to Sham key waqt mainey apney kapdey pehney aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur aap sey iskey mutalliq puchha. aap ney mujhey fatwaa diya ke jab tu ney bachcha jana to teri iddat puri ho gaee thi. aur aap ney mujhey apni marzi key mutabiq nikah karney ki ijazat di.
3549,"Hazrat Zufr bin Aus bin Hadsaan Nasri sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Sanaabil bin Ba'kak bin Sabaaq (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Sabeeaa Aslamiya (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha : teri iddat khatam nahin hogi yahan tak ke chaar maah das din guzar jaeyn, yani dono iddaton mein sey aakhiri iddat. chunanche wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aayin aur aap sey iskey mutalliq puchha. unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey fatwaa diya ke main waza' hamal key baad nikah kar sakti hun. jab unka khawind (shohar) faut huwa to wo hamal key nawen mahiney mein thin. wo Hazrat Saad bin khaula (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thin jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hajjatul-wadaa mein faut ho gaey they. to jab Hazrat Sabeeaa ney bachcha jana to unhoney apni qom key eik jawan shakhs sey nikah kar liya."
3550,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Utba ney umr bin Abdullah bin Arqam Zohri ko likha ke aap Sabeeaa binte Haris Aslamiya key paas jaeyn aur un sey poochhen ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen unkey hamal key silsiley mein kya irshad farmaya tha? Hazrat umr bin Abdullah unkey paas gaey aur un sey puchha to unhoney batlaya ke wo Hazrat Saad bin khaula (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thi. wo Sahabi Rasool they. Badr mein shareek huye they. Hajjatul-wadaa mein faut ho gaey to us ney un ki wafat key baad chaar maah das din guzarney sey pehley hi bachcha jan diya. jab wo nifaas sey pak hui to uskey paas Abu-Sanaabil aaye jo banu Abduddaar sey talluq rakhtey they. unhoney usey zeb aur zeenat ki haalat mein dekha to kaha : shayad to nikah ka irada rakhti hai jab ke abhi chaar maah das din nahin guzrey. jab mainey Abu-Sanaabil sey ye baat suni to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur aap sey pura waqia keh sunaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tujhey bachcha paida huwa tha, teri iddat khatam ho gaee thi."
3551,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin bayan kartey hain ke main Koofa shehar mein ansaar ki eik bahut badi majlis mein betha tha. un mein Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Laila bhi mojud they. haazirin ney Hazrat Sabeeaa (Raziallahu anha) ka waqia zikr kiya. mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Utba bin Masood sey zikr kiya ke jab bachcha paida ho to aurat ki iddat khatam ho jati hai. Hazrat ibne abi Laila kehney lagey : lekin unkey chacha (Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) to iskey qaail nahin. mainey zara buland aawaz mein kaha : agar main Hazrat Abdullah bin Utba par bohtan baandhon jab ke wo Koofa shehar mein zinda mojud hain, phir to main bahut be-baak hun? phir main apney ustaad Hazrat Malik sey mila. mainey kaha ke Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Sabeeaa key barey mein kya farmatey they? Malik kehney lagey ke unhoney farmaya : kya tum is par sakhti kartey ho, narmi nahin kartey? chhoti Sura Nisa (Soora Talaq) badi Sura Nisa sey baad utri hai."
3552,"Hazrat Alqama bin Qais sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jo shakhs chahey mein us sey mubaahala kar sakta hun ke aayat : (وَاُولاَتُ الْاَحْمَالِ … ),''hamal wali aurton ki iddat ye hai ke wo bachcha jan den.'' is aayat sey baad utri hai jis mein us aurat ki iddat bayan ki gaee hai jiska khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya ho, lihaza jis aurat ka khawind faut ho jaey, jab usey bachcha paida ho jaey to uski iddat khatam ho jati hai. ye alfaz Maimoon bin Abbas key hain."
3553,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke chhoti Sura Nisa (Soora Talaq) Sura Baqra key baad nazil hui.
3554,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey eik aadmi key barey mein puchha gaya jisney eik aurat sey shaadi ki, mehar muqarrar nahin kiya aur us sey jima (sambhog) bhi nahin kiya ke mar gaya. Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is ko us jaisi dusri aurton ki tarah mehar milega, na kam na ziyada, usey iddate-wafat bhi guzaarni hogi aur usey virasat bhi milegi. itney mein Hazrat Ma'qil bin Sanaan Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur farmaney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari eik aurat Barwaa' binte Washiq key barey mein aap key faisley jaisa faisla farmaya tha. Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ye sun kar bahut khush huye."
3555,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat key liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey. albatta khawind (shohar) par (woh chaar maah das din tak sog keregi)."
3556,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat Allah Taala par aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti hai, uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo khawind (shohar) key ilawa kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey."
3557,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko is member par farmatey suna : jo aurat Allah Taala par aur uskey Rasool par eman rakhti hai, uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey. albatta wo khawind (shohar) par chaar maah das din sog keregi."
3558,Hazrat Faariaa binte Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mera khawind (shohar) apney ajmi (ghair Arabi) ghulamon ki talash mein nikla. unhoney usey pakad kar qatl kar diya. us waqt meri rihaaish eik door daraz ghar mein thi. main aur merey do bhai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur aap sey soorate-haal zikr ki. aap ney mujhey us ghar sey muntaqil honey ki ijazat dey di lekin jab main wapis janey ko mudi to aap ney bula-kar farmaya : apney ghar hi mein raho yahan tak ke iddat puri ho jaey.
3559,"Hazrat Faariaa binte Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke merey khawind (shohar) ney kuchh ajmi (ghair Arabi) ghulam kisi kaam key liye kiraey par liye. unhoney usey qatl kar diya. mainey ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki aur arz kiya ke main apney khawind (shohar) key zaati ghar mein nahin reh rahi. aur mujhey uski taraf sey koi nafqa (bharan-poshan) waghera bhi nahin milta to kya main aur merey yatim bachchey merey maykey mein muntaqil ho jaeyn? main wahan in bachchon ki dekh bhaal bhi karungi. aap ney farmaya : aisey kar lo. phir aap ney farmaya : tu ney kaisey kaha tha? mainey dobara puri baat batai to aap ney farmaya : jahan tujhey wafat ki khabar pahunchi hai, wahin iddat puri kar."
3560,Hazrat Faariaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mera khawind (shohar) apney ajmi ghulamon ki talash mein nikla. usey qudoom ke maqam par qatl kar diya gaya. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap key samney apney meykey muntaqil honey ka zikr kiya aur apni majburi bayan ki. aap ney pehley to mujhey rukhsat (chhoot) inayat farma di lekin jab main wapis chali to mujhey bulaya aur farmaya : apney usi ghar mein thehri-reh yahan tak ke muqarrara iddat puri ho jaey.
3561,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke is aayat ney aurat key liye khawind (shohar) key ghar iddat guzarney ko mansookh (radd) kar diya hai. ab wo jahan chahey iddat guzar sakti hai. is aayat sey murad hai Allah Taala ka farman (غَیْرَ اِخْرَاجْ),''yani aurton ko dorane-iddat mein gharon sey nikala na jaey, wo khud chali jaeyn to koi harj nahin.''"
3562,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hamsheera Hazrat Furaiaa binte Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke mera khawind (shohar) qudoom jagah mein qatl ho gaya. chunanche main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur kaha ke hamara ghar door daraz jagah mein hai (mujhey meykey muntaqil honey ki ijazat di jaey). aap ney ijazat dey di, phir bulaya aur farmaya : apney ghar hi mein chaar maah das din thehar yahan tak ke muqarrara iddat puri ho jaey."
3563,"Hazrat Zainab binte Abi Salma farmati hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) key yahan hazir hui jab unkey walid mohtaram Hazrat Abu-Sufiyaan bin Harab (Raziallahu anhu) faut huye they. chunanche unhoney khushbu mangwai aur eik bachchi ko lagai, phir khushbu waley haath apney rukhsaaron par mal liye aur farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu laganey ki koi zarurat nahin thi magar mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo aurat Allah par aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti hai uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din sey zayed sog karey magar khawind (shohar) par chaar maah das din tak sog karna hoga. Hazrat Zainab ney kaha : phir main Hazrat Zainab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan hazir hui jab unkey bhai faut huye. unhoney bhi khushbu mangwai aur lagai, phir farmaney lagin : Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu ki koi zarurat nahin thi magar mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko member par farmatey sun rakha hai : jo aurat Allah Taala par aur aakhirat par eman rakhti hai uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din sey zayed sog kerey. albatta khawind (shohar) par wo chaar maah das din sog kerey. Hazrat Zainab ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko farmatey suna ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri beti ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya hai. ab uski aankh mein takleef hai. kya main usey surma dal dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, 'phir aap ney farmaya : sirf chaar maah das din hi to hain jabkey daure-jahiliyat mein aurat saal key baad mengni phenka karti thi. (raawi hadees) Hazrat Humed ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Zainab sey puchha : saal key baad mengni phainkney ka matlab kya hai? unhoney farmaya : jab kisi aurat ka khawind (shohar) faut ho jata tha to wo eik tang aur gandey sey chhappar mein dakhil ho jati aur gandey kapdey pehan leti. na khushbu lagaati, na koi aur safai ki chiz yahan tak ke usey eik saal guzar jata, phir uskey paas koi janwer, gadhaa, bakri ya koi perinda laya jata aur wo (aurat) uskey sath apna jism malti. junhi wo us janwer sey apna jism malti, wo janwer mar jata, phir wo us chhappar sey bahar nikalti. usey eik mengni di jati to wo us ko peechhey sey phainkti, phir wo uskey baad khushbu waghera jo chahti lagaati. Hazrat Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (تَفْتَضُّ) key maana hain : wo milti thi. aur Muhammad ki hadees mein Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke hafsh key maana jhaunpdi key hain."
3564,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aurat kisi maiyat par teen din sey zayed sog na kerey. albatta khawind (shohar) par chaar maah das din kerey. wo koi shaukh-rang daar kapda na pehney. na dhaari daar kapda pehney. na surma daley. na kanghi kerey. na khushbu lagaey magar jab wo haiz sey pak ho to kuchh qust ya azfaar khushbu laga sakti hai.
3565,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aurat ka khawind faut ho jaey wo (iddat key doran mein) kasnabey sey ranga huwa zard kapda aur gairu sey ranga huwa surkh kapda na pehney, na wo mahndi lagaey na surma."
3566,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat Allah Taala par aur aakhirat par eman rakhti hai, uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo khawind (shohar) key ilawa kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey. (dorane-sog) wo (bewa aurat) surma na lagaey, mahndi na lagaey aur banai key baad ranga huwa kapda na pehney."
3567,"Hazrat Ummey Hakim binte Usaid apni walida mohtarma sey bayan karti hain ke unka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya aur unhen aakhon mein takleef thi. wo surma dal liya karti thin, phir unhoney apni londi ko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key paas bheja aur un sey surma dalney key barey mein puchha. unhoney farmaya ke sog wali aurat surma nahin dal sakti magar shadeed majburi key waqt (jab surma daley baghair chaara na ho). jab merey khawind Hazrat Abu-Salma faut huye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik dafa merey paas tashrif laye jab ke mainey aakhon par aelwa laga rakha tha. aap ney farmaya : Umme-Salma ! ye kya hai? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye sirf aelwa hai. is mein koi khushbu waghera nahin. aap ney farmaya : ye chehrey ko Hasan aur ronaq bakhshta hai, lihaza raat key ilawa isey na lagaya kar aur kisi khushbudar tel ya mahndi key sath kanghi na kiya kar kyonkey ye rang (wali zeenat) hai. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! to kis chiz key sath kanghi kiya karun? farmaya : beeri key pattey sar par baandh liya kar, phir kanghi kar liya kar."
3568,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik quraishi aurat aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri beti ki aankhen dukhney lagi hain to kya main usey surma dal dun? us ka khawind (shohar) faut ho chuka tha. aap ney farmaya : chaar maah das din tak nahin dal sakti. wo kehney lagi : mujhey uski nazar ka khatra hai. aap ney farmaya : hergiz nahin, chaar maah das din mein nahin. jahiliyat mein us jaisi aurat ko apney khawind (shohar) par eik saal tak sog karna padta tha, phir saal key ikhtitaam (khaatmey) par wo mengni phenka karti thi."
3569,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur apni beti key barey mein puchha jis ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya tha aur usey aakhon ki takleef thi. aap ney farmaya : jahiliyat key daur mein aisi aurton ko eik saal tak sog karna padta tha, phir saal key baad wo mengni phainkti thi. ab to iddat sirf chaar maah das din hai."
3570,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik quraishi aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kehney lagi ke meri beti ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya hai. mujhey uski aakhon ka khatra hai. us ka maqsad surme ki ijazat hasil karna tha. aap ney farmaya : is sey pehley tum mein sey aisi aurat eik saal key baad mengni phenka karti thi. ab to iddat sirf chaar maah das din hai. raawi ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Zainab sey puchha : saal key baad mengni phainkney ka kya matlab hai? unhoney farmaya : jahiliyat mein jab kisi aurat ka khawind faut ho jata to wo apney sab sey gandey ghar mein ja kar beth jati yahan tak ke jab usey eik saal guzar jata to wo nikalti aur apney peechhey mengni phainkti.
3571,"Hazrat Zainab sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Hazrat Umme-Salma aur Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke kya aurat apney khawind ki iddate-wafat key doran mein surma dal sakti hai? wo kehney lagin ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai thi aur us ney uskey mutalliq puchha tha. aap ney farmaya tha : daure-jahiliyat mein jab kisi aurat ka khawind (shohar) faut ho jata tha to wo eik saal tak thehri rehti thi, phir apney peechhey mengni phainkti aur nikalti. ab to iddat sirf chaar maah das din hai, lihaza wo surma nahin dal sakti yahan tak ke ye muddat guzar jaey."
3572,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aurat ko jis ka khawind (shohar) faut ho gaya ho, tuhur (paaki) key waqt qust aur azfaar khushbu istimal karney ki ijazat di hai."
3573,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Allah Taala key is farman :(وَالَّذِیْنَ یُتَوَفَّوْنَ مِنْکُمْ … غَیْرَ اِخْرَاجٍ),""jo log qaribul-maut hon aur un ki biwiyan zinda hon to wo marney sey pehley apni biwiyon key liye wasiyat kar jaeyn ke unhen eik saal tak kharch diya jaeyn, isi ke sath unhen ghar sey na nikala jaey.''key barey mein farmaya ke ye hukm virasat ki aayat sey mansookh (radd) hai jis mein unkey liye chotha ya aathwan hissa muqarrar kiya gaya hai. aur eik saal ki muddat bhi mansookh (radd) hai kyonkey un ki iddat chaar maah das din tak muqarrar kar di gaee hai."
3574,"Hazrat Ikrima ney Allah Taala key farman : (وَالَّذِیْنَ یُتَوَفَّوْنَ مِنْکُمْ … غَیْرَ اِخْرَاجٍ),''jo log qaribul-maut hon aur un ki biwiyan zinda hon to wo marney sey pehley apni biwiyon key liye wasiyat kar jaeyn ke unhen eik saal tak kharch diya jaeyn, aur unhen ghar sey na nikala jaey.''key barey mein farmaya ke is aayat ko us (dusri) aayat ney mansookh (radd) kar diya : (وَالَّذِیْنَ یُتَوَفَّوْنَ مِنْکُمْ … أَرْبَعَۃَ أَشْہُرٍ وَعَشْرًا),""jo log faut ho jaeyn aur un ki biwiyan zinda hon to biwiyan chaar maah das din tak apney aap ko (idhar-udhar janey, zeb aur zeenat karney aur nikah waghera sey) rok kar rakhen."
3575,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Aasim sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anhu), jo ke banu Makhzoom key eik aadmi key nikah mein thi, ney mujhey bataya ke merey khawind (shohar) ney mujhey aakhiri Talaq dey di. wo kisi jang ko gaey huye they. unhoney apney wakeel ko hukm diya ke mujhey kuchh kharch waghera ada kerey. mainey unhen kam mehsus kiya. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi zauja (biwi) mutahra key paas gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to main unkey paas hi thi. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye Fatima binte Qais hai. iskey khawind (shohar) ney isey Talaq dey di hai aur kuchh khrcha bhi bheja hain lekin is ney (kam samajh kar) qubul nahin kiya jab ke khawind ka khayal hai ke mainey ye bhi bator ehsan bheja hai. aap ney farmaya : wo durust kehta hai. phir aap ney farmaya : to Umme-Kulsum key ghar chali ja aur wahan iddat guzar. phir aap ney farmaya : Umme-Kulsum key paas aaney janey walon ki kasrat rehti hai, lihaza to Abdullah bin Ummey Maktoom key yahan muntaqil ho ja. wo na-bina shakhs hai. main unkey ghar muntaqil ho gaee aur wahin iddat guzari. jab iddat khatam hui to Abu-Jahm aur Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan ney mujhey nikah key pegham bhejey. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap sey is barey mein mashwara kiya to aap ney farmaya : Abu-Jahm key barey main to mujhey khatra hai ke uski lathi har waqt harkat mein raheygi. baqi raha Muawiya ! to wo maali lihaz sey faqir hai. baad mein mainey Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) sey nikah kar liya."
3576,Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Abu-Amr bin Hafs bin Mughira key nikah mein thi. unhoney mujhey teen mein sey aakhiri Talaq bhej di. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur khawind (shohar) key ghar sey muntaqil honey key barey mein puchha. aap ney mujhey Hazrat ibne Ummey Maktoom (jo naa-beeney they) key ghar muntaqil honey key liye farmaya. Marwan ney (apney daure-hukoomat mein) Hazrat Fatima ke is masley mein tasdeeq nahin ki ke aisi mutallaqa khawind (shohar) key ghar sey muntaqil ho sakti hai. Urwa kehtey hain ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney bhi Hazrat Fatima ki is baat ko taslim nahin kiya tha.
3577,"Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, kehti hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey khawind ney mujhey teen talaaqein dey di hain (yani alag alag) mujhey khatra hai ke koi chor chakaar deewar na phalang aaye, lihaza aap ney mujhey ijazat dey di aur main khawind (shohar) key ghar sey muntaqil ho gaee."
3578,Hazrat Sh'abi sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey unkey barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key faisley ki baabat puchha to unhoney bataya : mujhey merey khawind (shohar) ney aakhiri Talaq dey di thi. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat aaliya mein uskey khilaf rihaaish aur kharch (dorane-iddat) ka daawey kar diya lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey rihaaish aur kharch nahin dilwaye aur mujhey ibne Ummey Maktoom key yahan iddat guzarney ka hukm diya.
3579,"Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, kehti hain ke merey khawind (shohar) ney mujhey Talaq dey di. mainey khawind (shohar) key ghar sey muntaqil honey ka irada kar liya. chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to aap ney farmaya : apney chacha key betey Amr bin Ummey Maktoom key ghar muntaqil ho ja aur wahan iddat puri kar. (ye sun kar) Hazrat Aswad ney Hazrat Sh'abi ko kankar maar kar kaha : to marey ! aisa fatwaa kyon deta hai? Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya tha : agar to do gawah ley aaye jo gawahi den ke asiliyat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey hamney ye baat suni hai to theek hai warna hum eik aurat key kehney sey Allah Taala ki kitab ka ye hukm nahin chhod saktey : (لاَ تُخْرِجُوْھُنَّ … بِفَاحِشَۃٍ مُبَیِّنَۃٍ),''talaq paai hui aurton ko gharon sey na nikalo aur na wo khud muntaqil hon, siwaey iske ke wo kisi wazeh burai ka irtikab kar bethen.''"
3580,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke meri khaala ko Talaq ho gaee. unhoney apney nakhlistan mein jana chah. eik aadmi unhen mila to usney unhen rok diya. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin to aap ney farmaya : to ja kar apni khajuron ka phal tod sakti hai? ho sakta hai to us sey sadqa karey ya koi aur nek kaam kerey.
3581,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Hafs ney kaha ke main aur Hazrat Abu-Salma Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) key paas hazir huyi. wo farmaney lagin : mujhey merey khawind (shohar) ney aakhiri Talaq dey di, mujhey rihaaish aur pura nafqa (bharan poshan) na diya balke apney eik chacha zaad bhai key paas merey liye das qafeez rakh chhodey : paanch gehun key aur paanch jau key. chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur is barey mein baat ki to aap ney farmaya : wo durust kehta hai. aur mujhey kisi key ghar mein iddat guzarney ka hukm diya. unhen unkey khawind (shohar) ney Talaqe-baaina (jiskey baad jima (sambhog) mumkin na ho) dey di thi."
3582,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Utba sey riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Amr bin Usman ney Saeed bin Zaid ki beti ko bitta (teesri) Talaq dey di. is ki walida ka naam Hamna binte Qais tha. chunanche uski khaala Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney usey Abdullah bin Amr key ghar sey muntaqil honey ka hukm diya. Hazrat Marwan ney bhi ye baat sun li. unhoney usey pegham bheja aur iddat khatam honey tak wapis apney ghar janey ka hukm diya. us ney unhen wapsi pegham bheja ke mujhey meri khaala Hazrat Fatima ney ye fatwaa diya hai aur bataya hai ke jab unhen unkey khawind abu-Amr bin Hafs Makhzoomi ney Talaq dey di thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen khawind (shohar) key ghar sey muntaqil honey ka hukm diya tha. Hazrat Marwan ney Hazrat Qabeesa bin Zuaib ko Hazrat Fatima ki taraf bheja aur uskey mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : main Hazrat Abu-Amr key nikah mein thi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen mein Ameer muqarrar farmaya to mera khawind (shohar) bhi unkey sath gaya aur wahan sey us ney Talaq bhej di aur ye aakhiri Talaq thi jo baqi thi, isi ke sath us ney hazraat Haris bin Hisham aur Ayaash bin Abi Rabeea ko mujhey nafqa (bharan poshan) deney ko kaha. mainey hazraat Haris aur Ayaash ko pegham bheja ke merey khawind (shohar) ka bheja huwa naan aur nafqa mujhey den, to unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamarey zimmey tera koi nafqa (bharan poshan) nahin siwaey iske ke to hamila ho. aur to hamari ijazat key baghair hamari rihaaish-gaah mein bhi nahin reh sakti. Hazrat Fatima ney kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap sey sari soorate-haal bayan ki to aap ney un ki tasdeeq ki. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kahan muntaqil ho jaaun? aap ney farmaya : to ibne Ummey Maktoom key yahan chali ja. wo na-bina shakhs hain jin ki wajeh sey Allah Taala ney apni Kitab (Quran Majeed) main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par izhar narazi farmaya tha. main unkey yahan muntaqil ho gaee. main unkey yahan faaltu kapdey utaar sakti thi yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mera nikah Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey kar diya."
3583,Hazrat Fatima binte Abi Habish (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur apney (be-qaeyda) khoon ki shikayat ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye eik bimari hai. ghor kiya kar. jab tujhey haiz aaye to namaz na padh aur jab tera haiz guzar jaey Tu Pak ho aur aglaa haiz aaney tak namaz padhti reh.
3584,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey Allah Taala key farman :(ما نَنْسَخْ مِنْ اٰیَۃٍ ... اَوْ مِثْلِھَا),''jo aayat hum mansookh kar den ya bhula den, hum us sey behtar ya kam se kam us jaisi aayat aur ley aatey hain.''  aur (وَاِذَا بَدَّلَنَآ اٰیَۃً … بِمَا یُنَزَّلُ), ''jab hum kisi aayat ki jagah koi aur aayat ley aatey hain aur Allah Taala apni utaari hui aayaton ko khub janta hai … الخ.'' aur (یَمْحُوا اللّٰہُ … اُمُّ الْکِتَابِ),''Allah taala jo chahey mita deta hai aur jo chahey baqi rakhta hai aur uskey paas hi asal kitab hai.'' key barey mein farmaya ke Quran Majeed mein sab sey pehley qibla mansookh (radd) huwa isi tarah farmaya : (وَالْمُطَلَّقٰتُ یَتَرَبَّصْنَ … اِنْ اَرَادُوْآ اِصْلاَحًا),''Talaq shuda aurten teen haiz tak apney aap ko roke rakhen aur unkey liye ye jayez nahin ke us chiz ko chhupaeyn jo Allah Taala ney unkey reham mein paida farmaee hai (aakhir aayat tak).''pehley ye dastoor tha ke koi aadmi jab apni biwi ko Talaq deta to wo us sey ruju ka haq rakhta tha, chahey teen talaaqein hi dey chuka ho. Allah Taala ney us dastoor ko mansookh (radd) farma diya aur farmaya : (اَلطَّلاَقُ مَرَّتَانِ ... اَوْ تَسْرِیْحٌ بِاِحْسَانٍ),''razaee Talaq do dafa hi hai. rakhna hai to achchhey tareeqey sey rakhey warna achchhey tareeqey sey chhod dey.''"
3585,Hazrat Yunus bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke mainey apni biwi ko Talaq dey di jab ke wo haiz sey thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key yahan hazir huye aur aap ko ye baat batai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kaho ke us sey ruju kerey. jab wo pak ho jaey to phir chahey to Talaq dey dey. mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke kya wo Talaq shumar ki gaee ? unhoney farmaya : aur kya ! tum batao ke agar Talaq deney wala sahih Talaq sey aajiz raha aur us ney himaqat kar di to kya Talaq shumar nahin hogi?
3586,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye baat zikr ki. aap ney farmaya : usey kaho ke us sey ruju karey yahan tak ke usey eik haiz aur aaye, phir jab wo pak ho jaey to agar wo chahey to usey Talaq dey dey, chahey rakh ley. ye wo Talaq hai jis ka Allah Taala ney hukm diya hai. Allah Taala ney farmaya : « { فَطَلَّقْوْھُنَّ لِعِدَّتِھِنَّ }  aurton ko unkey sahih waqt mein Talaq do."
3587,"Hazrat Naafey (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey jab us shakhs key barey mein puchha jata jisney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq di to wo farmatey : agar us ney pehli ya dusri Talaq di hai to ( wo ruju karey kyonkey ) mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya tha ke us sey ruju kar, phir usey apney paas rakh yahan tak ke usey eik aur haiz aaye, phir wo pak ho to ab chahey to usey jima sey pehley Talaq dey dey. aur agar tu ney teesri Talaq di hai to tu ney aurat ko Talaq deney key barey mein Allah Taala key hukm ki nafarmani ki hai. aur teri biwi tujh sey juda ho gaee."
3588,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ruju ka hukm diya, lihaza unhoney ruju kar liya."
3589,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jisney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq di thi. unhoney farmaya : to Abdullah bin umr ko janta hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya is ney bhi apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur aap ko ye baat batai, chunanche aap ney usey hukm diya ke us sey ruju karey yahan tak ke wo pak ho to phir chahey to Talaq dey dey. ( raawi hadees Abdullah bin Taoos ney kaha ke ) mainey is sey ziyada, us (apney baap) sey nahin suna."
3590,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hafsa ko Talaq dey di thi, phir aap ney ruju farma liya tha. « wallahu-aalam » ."
